('21 DAYS TO A NEW HEALTHY YOU! How I lost 170lbs (ONLINE WEIG', '&#34;IT&#39;S TIME FOR YOU TOÂ BOUNCE BACK!!&#34; \nEvent Date: February 01, 2015 to December 31, 2015 \nA Global Online &#34;21-DAY CHALLENGE&#34; Weight-Loss and Weight-Management Program for MEN and WOMEN \nÂ For busy moms, dads, students, children, executives, business owners, teachers and the likeÂ  \nÂ  Â  Â Â  \nÂ  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â Photograph by Peter Yang. \nSometimes you need to give your body a rest from what you have been eating regularly, such as meats, especially those that take quite a bit of time to digest and to rid the body of toxins that came in through certain foods eaten. Â Over the last eight years I have faced obesity twice and have journaled my progress to freedom. Â  \nÂ  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â Â  \nFurther, in writing several books to help others overcome obesity as well, I have now created online weight loss / nutrition and weight management &#34;events&#34; for those whom are &#34;on-the-go&#34;, have limited finances to join gyms and weight loss groups and programs and for those whom simply cannot afford to nor have the time to exercise 1-2 hours per day as well as endure the pounding that &#34;daily&#34; jogging puts on your knees. Â  My solutions to weight loss, weight management, nurition and getting your health back on track is for any one of any age. \nWithin my books I discuss how I lost 170lbs, beat obesity twice and sculpted an eating, workout and overall nutrition plan that can be done ANYWHERE. \n  \nHOW THIS WILL WORK: \nA) \nComplete the Registration for your FREE Eventbrite Ticket so we know you&#39;re participating in thisÂ ONLINEÂ (which you can do from anywhere in the World and on any device)Â WEIGHT LOSS CHALLENGE/PROGRAM \nB) Â TO OFFICIALLY PARTICIPATE IN THE &#34;PROGRAM&#34;: \nPurchase t