usiness in the next 100 days. \n  In the media \nMoonwalk and Moonwalk Tomorrow has been featured in several media, including: \nE24.no  \nTV2 Nyhetskanalen \nAftenposten ', '2015-11-26 18:00:00', 'Business & Professional', 'Venue to be announced', 'NO', 'oslo', 'TBA, Oslo, NO', 59.9138688, 10.7522454, 'http://www.eventbrite.com/e/moonwalk-tomorrow-demoday-tickets-19146220862?aff=ebapi', 'eventbrite', 'https://img.evbuc.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimg.evbuc.com%2Fhttp%253A%252F%252Fcdn.evbuc.com%252Fimages%252F16420737%252F128025948979%252F1%252Foriginal.jpg%3Frect%3D398%252C0%252C3202%252C1601%26s%3D88383d9aa70ac8c637159fa532fd54bd?h=200&w=450&s=e5142a4558b4bca61f94a0e3405ae30c'),
