ng, Buy & Hold, Rent or Least Options, No Money, No Credit Acquisition, Subject To Investing, Multi Units or Apartment Complexes, Seller Financed Notes, Commercial Investments, and much more! \n_ ', '2015-11-12 18:30:00', 'Business & Professional', 'Location Provided After Registration', 'US', 'New york', 'Madison ave., New York, US', 40.7127837, -74.0059413, 'http://www.eventbrite.com/e/nyc-real-estate-investor-orientation-tickets-6852045653?aff=ebapi', 'eventbrite', 'https://img.evbuc.com/http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.evbuc.com%2Fimages%2F1687699%2F62435817635%2F1%2Foriginal.jpg?h=200&w=450&s=8f621dcf5cbf0430eb4e526189f98efb');
